project_overview.name: Sakila Database Film Rental Project
project_overview.purpose: A web application that provides a front end for the Sakila database, allowing users to browse films and actors, manage rentals, and view personal account information.

main_components.name: Controllers
main_components.description: Handle incoming requests and manage the flow of data between the view and the model.

main_components.name: Entities
main_components.description: Represent the data model for the application, including films, actors, customers, and rentals.

main_components.name: Repositories
main_components.description: Provide an abstraction layer for data access, allowing interaction with the database.

main_components.name: Services
main_components.description: Contain the business logic of the application, coordinating between controllers and repositories.

main_components.name: Security Configuration
main_components.description: Manage user authentication and authorization, ensuring secure access to different parts of the application.
